{"about_the_game":"Is the next member of Congress a werewolf? Can you survive a lycanthrope's bite? There\u2019s no silver bullet for winning an election!<br><br><i>Congresswolf</i> is an interactive novel by Ellen Cooper, where your choices control the story. It's entirely text-based--140,000 words, without graphics or sound effects--and fueled by the vast, unstoppable power of your imagination.<br><br><i>&quot;Democracy must be something more than two wolves and a sheep voting on what to have for dinner.&quot; -- James Bovard</i><br><br>When a werewolf murders your boss, you must step up to run a Congressional campaign all on your own. While werewolves, protestors, and worse--the media--lurk around every corner, you'll use everything you can to get your candidate elected.<br><br>Email servers? Tax returns? Who cares. Election-season secrets and October surprises are nothing compared to the possibility that your candidate might be a werewolf...or that you might become one yourself.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as any gender, play as gay or straight<br></li><li> Set the right tone with your TV ads<br></li><li> Prep your candidate for debates<br></li><li> Impress big donors<br></li><li> Get out the vote<br></li><li> Find out who killed your predecessor<br></li><li> Decide where your candidate will stand on werewolf rights</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Lefty Victorious","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/547990/658b6851029fb75f7eb20b24ff801f34075778d9.jpg"},{"name":"Faith Triumphant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/547990/658b6851029fb75f7eb20b24ff801f34075778d9.jpg"},{"name":"Hawk Ascendant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/547990/658b6851029fb75f7eb20b24ff801f34075778d9.jpg"},{"name":"Gilda Vanquishing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/547990/658b6851029fb75f7eb20b2